  "texts": [
    "Even though there are still many unanswered problems about how to classify AD, DL technology is still quite successful.",
    "There are situations when a person can detect AD better than a medical practitioner.",
    "A scientific study has also focused on using DL algorithms to identify MCI signs in MRI brain scans to halt the disease's growth and protect human life for a better, more peaceful future.",
    "Frontiers in Computer Science frontiersin.org"
  ]
}